WarmDirt - The Greenhouse Box Temperature Controller

Here's a greenhouse box temperature controller for winter growing.

Requirements
    Sensors
        Temperature 
            Heated dirt
            Potted dirt
            Box interior air
            Box exterior air
        Humidity 
            Box Interior
        Ambient light
        Lid closed switch

    Control
        Heater
        DC Motor

    Communication
        XBEE

    Framework
        Arduino compatible using ATMEGA328P
        

